lead_paragraph: St. Louis quarterback Case Keenum was not taken out of a game despite being disoriented after he was knocked to the ground.

headline.print_headline: A Mishandled Concussion Leads to a Review of Protocol
headline.main: A Mishandled Concussion Leads to a Review of Protocol

snippet: St. Louis quarterback Case Keenum was not taken out of a game despite being disoriented after he was knocked to the ground.
abstract: NFL is looking into changing concussion protocol after St Louis Rams quarterback Case Keenum is found to have been kept in game after suffering concussion.
